<item>
            <title>[LU-11658] The cl_cache may be uninitialized while osc is activating</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11658</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The obd_set_info_async will be invoked with KEY_CACHE_SET to initialize cl_cache while normal osc setup. We don&apos;t call it when osc has been disabled since export has not been setup. But it still be missed while osc active and causes the client to crash. &lt;/p&gt;
