&lt;pre&gt;[3968842.116112] Lustre: MGC10.53.18.101@tcp: Connection restored to MGS (at 10.53.18.101@tcp)
[4195817.824439] BUG: unable to handle kernel NULL pointer dereference at           (null)
[4195817.824813] IP: [&amp;lt;ffffffffa0b934a5&amp;gt;] osc_lru_reserve+0x25/0x130 [osc]
[4195817.825016] PGD ec67e1067 PUD 112e776067 PMD 0
[4195817.825209] Oops: 0000 [#1] SMP

.....

